, we propose practical defense\nstrategies to mitigate DI attacks, reducing the attack success rates to as low\nas 0% and 0.02% for targeted and non-targeted attacks, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Mar 2021 08:40:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 Mar 2021 07:56:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-03"}
