ate them. Notwithstanding, our results suggest that\n$\\beta$ and $\\nu$ are considerably larger than the Ashkin-Teller exponents\nreported in numerical studies of the 2NN system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Mar 2021 12:47:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-31"}
